WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.298 --> 00:00:01.559
As nice as it would be

2
00:00:01.559 --> 00:00:03.457
for everything to be perfect,

3
00:00:03.457 --> 00:00:05.367
some orders come in wrong.

4
00:00:05.367 --> 00:00:06.931
You can have the wrong quantity

5
00:00:06.931 --> 00:00:08.487
or the wrong product.

6
00:00:08.487 --> 00:00:09.787
What do you do?

7
00:00:09.787 --> 00:00:13.079
When incorrect or improper invoices are received,

8
00:00:13.079 --> 00:00:14.681
they may be returned to the vendor

9
00:00:14.681 --> 00:00:16.289
within seven calendar days

10
00:00:16.289 --> 00:00:18.147
for general goods or services

11
00:00:18.147 --> 00:00:19.645
from invoice receipt.

